title: IELTS Trainer Practice Tests
description:
IELTS Trainer is the perfect companion for IELTS exam preparation. As well as six full practice tests, it offers easy-to-follow expert guidance and exam tips designed to guarantee exam success. The first two tests are fully guided with step-by-step advice on how to tackle each paper. Extra practice activities are informed by a bank of real candidate's exam papers and focus on areas where students typically need most help.

Publisher: CAMBRIDGE UNIVERSITY PRESS
Published: 11 April 2011
Format: Mixed media product 240 pages
ISBN 13: 9780521128209 
ISBN 10: 052112820X
